Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.90,0:01:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, Pop.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.73,0:01:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs15\pos(191.4,110.25)}{\bord0\frx0\fry344\frz356\pos(193.5,112.5)}{\shad0}{\fn微软雅黑\c&H120E09&\b1}凱文·安德伍德
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.65,0:01:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Been a while, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.08,0:02:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到車隊駛過來了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you see that motorcade roll up?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.78,0:02:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是首次有美國總統\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's the first time that the President of the United States
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.24,0:02:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來到加夫尼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}has visited Gaffney.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.92,0:02:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能相信嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can you believe it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.80,0:02:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有的選  我也不會來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, I wouldn't be here if I had a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.60,0:02:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我現在得做這種事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I have to do these sort of things now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.42,0:02:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我顯得更有人情味\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Makes me seem more human.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.23,0:02:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做總統就得有點人情味\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you have to be a little human when you're the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.61,0:02:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他都沒錢給自己買墓碑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He couldn't even afford to pay for his own gravestone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.07,0:02:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用自己桑蒂諾軍事學院的獎學金買的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I paid for it out of my own scholarship money from The Sentinel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.69,0:02:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他葬禮那天只有我去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nobody showed up for his funeral except me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.71,0:02:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我母親都沒去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not even my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.82,0:02:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我要告訴你  爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I'll tell you this, though, Pop:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.40,0:02:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我下葬的時候  絕不會是葬在自家後院\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when they bury me, it won't be in my backyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.28,0:02:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等人們前來弔唁的時候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And when they come to pay their respects,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.33,0:02:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們得排隊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}they'll have to wait in line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.26,0:02:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該讓我們在墓地拍張照\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You should let us take a photo at the grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.60,0:02:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他想要點隱私  他可是在給父親掃墓啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He wants privacy. The man's honoring his father, for God's sakes.
