Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.98,0:04:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你要的信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here's the info you were looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.61,0:04:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們把那個安排在了下週二早上10點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And we have that scheduled for next Tuesday at 10 a.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.71,0:05:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's still good for you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.30,0:05:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  我會確認的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Excellent. I'll confirm it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.26,0:05:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.06,0:05:11.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.49,0:05:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.09,0:05:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總統可以見你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The president is ready to see you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.43,0:05:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天吶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.21,0:05:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我傷心欲絕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm devastated.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.37,0:05:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛他如子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I love this man as if he were my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.61,0:05:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是個鬥士  我相信他能挺過來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, he's a fighter, and I'm sure that he'll pull through.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.64,0:05:35.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都為他祈禱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our prayers are with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.37,0:05:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"...安德伍德總統昨日在一場新聞發佈會上如是說\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"...said President Underwood during a press conference yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.49,0:05:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬里蘭州警方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Maryland State Police
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.14,0:05:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和聯邦有關部門尚未找到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and Federal authorities have yet to locate
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.62,0:05:47.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯坦普先生的車或提出任何嫌疑人"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Stamper's car or name any suspects."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.68,0:05:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還想聽嗎  弟弟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You want more of this, brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.18,0:05:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許聽聽體育版吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or maybe the sports page?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.08,0:06:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"世界職業棒球大賽第六場比賽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Game Six of the World Series
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.08,0:06:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連續13局未得分\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}went scoreless for 13 innings
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.22,0:06:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊接著又因大雨延遲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}before a rain delay
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.79,0:06:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使這個已具有史詩性的夜晚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that turned an already epic evening
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.59,0:06:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足以載入史冊"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}into one for the history books."
