Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.24,0:06:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,31號病房需要醫生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need a doctor in room three-one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.14,0:06:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道格拉斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Douglas?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.48,0:06:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能聽到嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.53,0:07:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能聽到眨下眼睛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want you to blink if you can hear me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.15,0:07:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.49,0:07:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是蘭吉維尼醫生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My name is Dr. Lanjwani.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.63,0:07:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總統辦公室要求我親自看護你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The president's office asked me to look after you personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.23,0:07:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能得到最好的護理  好嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're getting the very best of care, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.65,0:07:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道格拉斯  如果你能感覺到  就眨眼睛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Douglas, I want you to blink if you can feel this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.32,0:07:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good. Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.67,0:07:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.43,0:07:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay. Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.56,0:07:40.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.32,0:07:46.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How about here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.62,0:07:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放鬆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.88,0:07:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放鬆  早期階段這很正常\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Relax. Perfectly normal at this early stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.59,0:07:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放鬆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.99,0:07:59.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.78,0:08:02.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  休息吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay. Get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.40,0:08:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是要傷害我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you gonna hurt me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.86,0:08:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你讓我幹什麼都行  求你別傷害我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will do whatever you want, please just don't hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.11,0:08:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-疼嗎  -有點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Does that hurt? - A little.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.27,0:08:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  我們開始吧  握拳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, let's go ahead. Try and make a fist for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.44,0:08:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-雷米  -什麼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Remy. - What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.64,0:08:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷米·丹頓  他在嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Remy Danton. Was he here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.03,0:08:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他來過  來看你怎麼樣了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He was. Just checking on your progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.32,0:08:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  握個拳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go ahead, make that fist for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.43,0:09:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獅子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.09,0:09:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犀牛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rhinoceros.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.13,0:09:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-駱駝  -很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Camel. - Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.00,0:09:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯道夫的鼻子什麼顏色\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What color is Rudolph's nose?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.84,0:09:13.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-魯道夫  -馴鹿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Rudolph? - Reindeer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.20,0:09:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅色\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Red.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.32,0:09:20.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是紅色的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's red.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.81,0:09:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美國總統\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The President of the United States?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.95,0:09:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道格拉斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Douglas?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.71,0:09:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美國總統是誰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who is the President of the United States?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗蘭克·安德伍德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Frank Underwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.39,0:09:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-今年是哪年  -2014年\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What year are we in? - 2014.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.12,0:09:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾月份\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What month is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.61,0:09:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,12月\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's December.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.34,0:09:55.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得回去工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have to get back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.99,0:10:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道格拉斯  聽我說\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Douglas. Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.74,0:10:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你遭受了有創骨折...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You suffered a compound fracture--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.95,0:10:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道我什麼毛病\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know what I fucking suffered!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.31,0:10:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好好聽我說\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need you to hear me this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.63,0:10:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你左額皮質遭到了損傷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There was damage to your left frontal cortex.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.70,0:10:13.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的運動技能將有退化\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your motor skills will be a struggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.93,0:10:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你將情緒多變\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your emotions will be unpredictable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.90,0:10:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前面的路很長  我們不能心急\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's a long road ahead, and we can't rush it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.68,0:10:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我們稍後做測試吧  -不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Let's do the test later. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.54,0:10:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就做完\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll finish it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.86,0:10:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你母親叫什麼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What was your mother's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.13,0:10:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她年輕漂亮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She was young and beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.04,0:10:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅各在她照看羊喝水時愛上了她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jacob fell in love with her while she was watering a lamb, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.19,0:10:42.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他做了七年的工\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}she became his wife after he worked seven years
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.05,0:10:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才終於娶到她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to earn her hand in marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.99,0:10:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推  腳跟向我手裏使勁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Push back. Heel into my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.79,0:10:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼吸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.48,0:10:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歸位  深呼吸  準備好了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Back up. Deep breath. Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.88,0:11:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推  用力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Push. Push.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.13,0:11:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道格\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.32,0:11:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中注意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.18,0:11:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天遞交國會的報告\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The report I submit to Congress today
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.14,0:11:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所包含的證據\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}includes evidence that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.18,0:11:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通常足以展開刑事檢控\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}would normally warrant criminal prosecution,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但鑒於總統特赦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but the Justice Department won't pursue charges
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.18,0:11:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司法部不會提出起訴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in accordance with the presidential pardons.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.81,0:11:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很感激鄧巴女士及其團隊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm grateful for the hard work Ms. Dunbar and her team
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.75,0:11:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對此次調查的盡心盡力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}have dedicated to their investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.31,0:11:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為回應  我將組建跨黨派委員會\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In response, I'll be forming a bipartisan commission
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.82,0:11:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研究競選籌款改革  以確保歷史不再重演\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to examine campaign finance reform so history does not repeat itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.08,0:11:35.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也讓我們國家癒合傷口\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and so that our nation can heal from these wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.40,0:11:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有培根芝士和普通的  你要哪種\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got bacon-cheese and regular. Which one you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.94,0:11:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.17,0:11:40.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還記得你以前從不吃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Remember when you'd never eat a burger
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.21,0:11:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有培根的漢堡嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if it didn't have bacon on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.39,0:11:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸會發火\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dad would get so pissed
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.95,0:11:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他討厭烤培根油的味兒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because he hated the smell of bacon grease on the grill.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.54,0:11:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在聽呢  加裏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm trying to listen, Gary.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.18,0:11:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總統也沒辦法  就讓他去死[燒]吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The president's hands are tied. Might as well let him burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.17,0:12:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs12\pos(220.8,216.9)\frz0.3223}{\bord0\pos(220.5,219.6)}{\shad2\c&H897D76&\4c&H3C1E13&\fn微软雅黑}改革不止需要一個委員會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.50,0:11:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們在準備棉花糖了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're getting their marshmallows ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.31,0:11:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看安德伍德的支持率\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look at Underwood's approval rating.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.21,0:11:58.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比沃克辭職之前的還糟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's worse than Walker's before he resigned.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.48,0:12:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要從那個坑裏爬出來  會很不容易\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's a deep, deep hole to climb out of.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.07,0:12:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共和黨會得意一陣了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Republicans are gonna have their fun for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.08,0:12:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普選時有很多可以拿來打擊他的東西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Plenty to hammer him on in the general.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.93,0:12:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且他們一心想傷人見血\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And they're out for blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.09,0:12:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教育和福利改革他們都輸得很慘\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They lost big on education and entitlement reform.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.19,0:12:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有  如果那些關於\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And if the rumors
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.35,0:12:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,《美國就業法案》的傳言是真...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}about America Works are true...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.23,0:12:13.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這計劃對左派太右\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For the left, that's just too far to the right
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.22,0:12:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對右派太左\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and for the right, it's too far to the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.13,0:12:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們需要我回去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They need me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.44,0:12:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裏  白宮嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where? The White House?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.12,0:12:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得扭轉局勢  開始為2016造聲勢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We got to turn the corner, start ramping up for 2016.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.99,0:12:23.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他或許能扭轉乾坤呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He might turn this around.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.28,0:12:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是真覺得他會贏吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't really think he's gonna win, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.23,0:12:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他經驗豐富  安德伍德有很多...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The guy's experienced. Underwood has a lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.02,0:12:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他會恢復的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He'll recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.67,0:12:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是個幕後推手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's a behind-the-scenes guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.09,0:12:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在聚光燈下不自在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's not comfortable in the spotlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.94,0:12:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如你先恢復吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How about you recover first?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.52,0:12:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...假意熱情  親吻嬰兒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...glad-handing and kissing babies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.73,0:12:38.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這證明了什麼  就是這18個月會很漫長\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is gonna be a long 18 months if this proves any indication.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.54,0:12:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會許下一堆空頭承諾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It can be a lot of chest-thumping
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.02,0:12:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但卻毫無建樹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but nothing really getting done.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.10,0:12:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解憂靈有助緩解抑鬱癥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Xybenetrin will help with depression.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.65,0:12:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丁螺環酮是治療焦慮的  給你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The buspirone is for anxiety. Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.19,0:12:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想給你開點止疼藥  但鑒於你的...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd like to prescribe you something for the pain, but with your...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.71,0:12:57.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有有癮史的病人...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, any patient with a history of addictive behavior--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.33,0:13:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂  沒事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know. It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.55,0:13:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼我撐得住\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can handle the pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.18,0:13:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他看上去好多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He looks a lot better.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.22,0:13:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  他還在睡呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, he's still asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.70,0:13:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得掛了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.28,0:13:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.52,0:13:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾你了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is this a bad time?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.51,0:13:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有  沒事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.76,0:13:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是沒人告訴我你要來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, it's just no one told me you were coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.19,0:13:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗蘭西斯要我代好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Francis sends his love.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.42,0:13:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他很想親自來  但是媒體...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He would visit himself, but with the media...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.61,0:14:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我懂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.66,0:14:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他之前來過的  那時...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He did come before, when...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.68,0:14:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我們倆都來過  -我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Both of us. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.30,0:14:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到花了  謝謝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I saw the flowers. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.11,0:14:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你看上去挺好  -我在好起來了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You look well. - I'm getting there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.02,0:14:13.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想好起來  好回去工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just want to get better so I can get back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.65,0:14:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都盼著呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're looking forward to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.16,0:14:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們真是需要一切幫助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can use all the help we can get, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.58,0:14:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我一直在看新聞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. Been watching the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.24,0:14:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗蘭西斯  他真是無計可施了  共和黨...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Francis, he's at his wit's end. The Republicans...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.91,0:14:26.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不肯給他一張他能簽的法案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}won't send him a single bill he can sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.47,0:14:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-民主黨也好不到哪去  -鮑勃·博奇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- And the Democrats aren't much better. - Bob Birch?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.54,0:14:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞎子給蠢貨帶路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Blind leading the stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.79,0:14:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷米幹得還好嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How's Remy working out?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.31,0:14:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們更希望是你在  但他還不錯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, we'd much rather have you there, but he's doing a fine job.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.75,0:14:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道格  你...記得什麼嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Doug, do you... recall anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.50,0:14:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-關於事發經過  -怎麼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- About what happened? - Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.49,0:14:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察有什麼發現嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did the police find something?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.59,0:14:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據我們所知是沒有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not that we're aware of.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.75,0:14:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們叫他們暫時不要訊問你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And we've asked them to hold off questioning you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.77,0:14:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到你感覺好一些\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}until you're feeling more like yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.71,0:15:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞秋  她...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rachel, she...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.61,0:15:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不記得了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.82,0:15:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  你記得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.37,0:15:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是劫車\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A carjacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.62,0:15:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-是個男人  -什麼樣的男人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- A man. - What sort of man?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.79,0:15:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那部分記不清了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That part's fuzzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.13,0:15:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就可能是任何人了  誰都可能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It could be anyone, then. Any man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.99,0:15:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  誰都可能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. Any man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.28,0:15:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他被嚇跑了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And he got frightened?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.71,0:15:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去追他  然後就記不得了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I chased him and that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.41,0:15:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道她在哪嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Any idea where she is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.54,0:15:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.23,0:15:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一定得找到她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because it's important that we find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.28,0:15:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I really don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.41,0:15:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.26,0:15:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把這些都告訴警察\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want you to tell all of this to the police,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.37,0:15:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟我說的原話\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}exactly what you told me,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:15:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於劫車  那個男人  別提她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}about the carjacking and the man. Nothing about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.74,0:15:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.46,0:16:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你如果需要什麼  或記起了什麼...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you need anything, or remember anything...
