Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.03,0:16:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.71,0:16:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試試這個  你做得很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's try this one. You're doing a great job.
