Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.45,0:16:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.24,0:17:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  呼吸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good. Breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.33,0:17:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  不錯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Excellent. Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.15,0:17:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一個\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.30,0:17:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Great job.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.79,0:17:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一次  就好了  準備好了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One more time. It's almost done. Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.45,0:17:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持呼吸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Keep breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.08,0:17:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只記得他的聲音  他說"下車"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just his voice. He said, "Get out of the car."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.03,0:17:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能描述一下他的聲音嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anything you can say about the voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.61,0:17:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,形容下口音  咬字  音調高低\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Was it, uh... Accent? Lisp? High? Low?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.32,0:17:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深沉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.93,0:17:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就記得這些了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's all I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.78,0:17:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後我鳴了笛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then I laid on the horn. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.72,0:17:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得他跑了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I remember him running.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.89,0:17:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很模糊  我下了車\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Like a blur, I got out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.86,0:17:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去追他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I chased him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.48,0:17:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不確定  我一定...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not sure. I must have...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.15,0:17:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去馬里蘭州那裏做什麼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What were you doing in that part of Maryland?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.74,0:17:50.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯坦普先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Stamper?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.11,0:17:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先生  你去馬里蘭州那裏做什麼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir. What were you doing in that part of Maryland?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.30,0:17:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有時候會開車思考\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I drive sometimes to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.33,0:18:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時工作上有很多事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There was a lot on my mind with work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.09,0:18:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是開車清理思緒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I drive to clear my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.26,0:18:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們找到車了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you found the car?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.05,0:18:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們目前只有你剛剛提供的信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We don't have anything other than what you just told us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.14,0:18:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的情緒最近如何  有過情緒爆發嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How's your mood been? Any episodes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.19,0:18:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有  藥物很好使\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. The meds are working.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.79,0:18:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是跟我說好聽的嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You just telling me what I want to hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.05,0:18:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  我感覺不錯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. I feel good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.83,0:18:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.14,0:18:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天就批准你出院\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna sign your release today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.14,0:18:30.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你一開始一定別太急躁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But it's important you take it easy at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.38,0:18:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都會變得難很多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everything's gonna be much harder in general.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.39,0:18:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.87,0:18:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人能照顧你嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you have someone who can look after you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.46,0:18:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有  我哥哥加裏從俄亥俄州過來了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. My brother Gary's in from Ohio.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.94,0:18:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  他能待多久\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good. How long is he here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.09,0:18:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-能待一陣吧  -好的  很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- A while, I guess. - Okay, great.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.96,0:18:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要去參加互助會\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's important you go to your meetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.94,0:18:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續保持不沾酒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stay on top of your sobriety.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.70,0:18:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿著這個  用來注射給你開的類固醇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take this. It's for the steroids I prescribed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.55,0:18:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每週一次  一針打在右腿大腿上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's one shot into the right thigh, once a week.
