Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.43,0:19:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再留兩周\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}while you transition back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.44,0:19:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該回你家人那裏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You should get back to your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.78,0:20:00.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  薩拉不介意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nah... Sarah's fine with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.13,0:20:02.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子們也是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The kids are, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.10,0:20:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加裏  我們都十年沒怎麼通話了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gary, we've hardly spoken in ten years.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.41,0:20:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經做了很多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've already gone above and beyond.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.32,0:20:11.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  你要我走嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right. You want me to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.63,0:20:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.83,0:20:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝你做的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thanks for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.08,0:20:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.61,0:20:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事打給我  我立刻坐飛機過來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, I'm just a phone call and a plane ticket away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.95,0:20:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路順風\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Safe travels.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.62,0:20:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保重\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.09,0:20:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加裏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, Gary, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.96,0:20:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我寄點孩子的照片來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Send me some pictures of the kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.14,0:20:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.53,0:21:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我欣賞你的一點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But one of the things I admire about you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.10,0:21:06.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在華盛頓特區\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is that in Washington, DC,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.24,0:21:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,效率這麼低的地方  你總能辦成事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}which is so gridlocked, you get things done.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.20,0:21:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據我所知  你有一項新的法案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I understand you've got, um, a new piece of legislation,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.12,0:21:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要推出一項重要的新法案  是什麼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a major new initiative you're rolling out. What is it?
